**LABS WHITE PAGE ROOT CAUSE:**

Hydration mismatch - SSR output doesn't match client render.

**FIX APPLIED:**
```javascript
import dynamic from 'next/dynamic';

const Component = dynamic(() => import('...'), {
  ssr: false,  // Disable SSR
  loading: () => <Skeleton />
});
```

All heavy components now use dynamic import with `ssr: false`. This prevents hydration errors from canvas/WebGL/random elements.
